  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But apparently, I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then my father found a job in [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Legnica, ?] which is approximately 50 miles from Zlotoryja.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Legnica, ?] he found a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We moved to [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Legnica. ?] In [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Legnica, ?] I start to go-- there was another Yiddish school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I start to go there, the fifth grade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I finish this-- finish that, the whole elementary school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then I went to high school, finished Yiddish high school, and later on became a teacher in this very school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was involved-- since the beginning I was involved in drama.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Legnica ?] was a bigger-- bigger city with a much bigger population.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Of course, you cannot compare the population.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "If [? we are ?] talking about bigger population, we're speaking about 400, 500, 600 souls.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's not like it was before the war, or even in the United States, the Jewish population lives in-- in an inner city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And please, I don't want to forget to say-- say how my father found out about his family and what we found out-- if we could find out about a family who perished in the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "During the war, my daddy was in the army, in the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I mentioned before, he fought the Germans [? on ?] the Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was wounded in-- in the leg while he was throwing a grenade to a tank.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was-- his stomach was-- was down, because he was carrying-- there was no transportation for the Russian Army at the beginning, specially in beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
